Athena:
-------
* IntroduceDQ2JobSplitter.filesize: splitting into subjobs of a maximum
  filesize sum (in MB)
  config['Athena']['MaxFileSizeNGDQ2JobSplitter']=5000
  config['Athena']['MaxFileSizePandaDQ2JobSplitter']=5000
  NG and Panda backend splitting has been restricted to a maximum of 5 GB
* Improve athena package setup on worker node
* Improve tarball packing 
* Fix typo in TNTJobSplitter environment variable setting
* Patches for MuonCalibStream dataaccess for FILE_STAGER and DQ2_COPY mode
* Patches for NG statistics collection
* DQ2JobSplitter: Revert logic: sites takes priority over cloud

AthenaMC:
--------
* Fix bug #45593: typo in AthenaMCDatasets.py causing bad file matching
* Small fixes

AMAAthena:
----------
* AMAAthenaLCGRTHandler.py: include the monitoring service
* StagerJobSplitter.py: internal code factorization
* ama_athena-utility.sh: fix sample file name of the FileStager

Tasks:
------
* handling of tasks is now more similar to jobs:
   tasks(3) instead of tasks.get(3)
   and tasks(3).remove() instead of tasks.remove(3)
* MCTask can now be initialized from generator, evgen or simul dataset
  The input dataset file numbers  are displayed in overview()
* AnaTask is now working correctly, uses DQ2JobSplitter internally
* All transforms are now read-only when submitted (similar to jobs)
* several updates and bugfixes

